data.description: Feature Spotlight: Kissimmee Gem!  GREAT PRICE REDUCTION FOR INMEDIATE SALE !   Step into this impeccable townhouse nestled in the heart of Kissimmee, Florida. Elegantly designed with meticulous attention to detail, this residence boasts pristine ceramic and laminated floors, giving it a modern yet warm ambiance.  In the culinary heart of this home, you'll be greeted by state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances - perfect for both the everyday chef and those special occasions. But the magic doesn't stop inside! Venture out to the beautifully crafted back porch, an oasis crafted to let you savor Florida's enviable weather, be it a tranquil morning coffee or an al fresco evening dinner.  And for those with an investor's eye, this property shines even brighter. With permissions for both short-term and long-term rentals, this townhouse is not only a dream home but a promising investment opportunity. Whether you're seeking a serene Floridian retreat or a lucrative investment, this Kissimmee marvel is the answer.  Don't miss out on this unparalleled offering. Join us and witness the fusion of luxury, comfort, and opportunity.
